<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Sep1922"><font color="red">21 September 1922</font>, <cite>BLHW</cite> (JJ to Harriet Weaver): I enclose also a letter from Mr Darantiere by which it would seem that it was decided to go ahead with the printing already twelve days ago and apparently without any mention of the revision of the text.</div>
